            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              In select cases, we take on custom system design or advanced AI-enabled projects where standard tools and configurations break down. These engagements are selective and scoped independently.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
